        About this item

        • Kenon is equipped with 4 custom made capacitors (heart parts). For whiskers and underneath. The illumination interval of Kenon is as low as 0.4 seconds (Lv.1 continuous mode) and a wide illumination area. That's why it's super speed!
        • Made in Japan: Manufactured at a factory in Japan. Uses a power cord that provides more stable power than rechargeable, and illuminates light according to the Japanese skin. Designed to be lightweight at only 4.2 oz (120 g) for extended use
        • [Payment Methods] Various payment methods are available for credit cards (bulk up to 3 to 24 times/ribbons), cash exchange, convenience store payment (convenience store/ATM/netbanking / Edy/electronic money), after-payment (payment), mobile payment, etc
        • (Can be Payed Separately) Credit cards can be purchased from approx. 2,909 yen to KE-NON! (Except for split card fees)
        • [Performance] Even though it is a salon-class high performance, the KE-NON is easy to use by anyone at home. This is a unisex Japanese light beauty container that has already ordered over 1.1 million units in Japan
        • Irradiation Range: The included super premium cartridge is a commercial class with the size of the irradiation port 1.4 x 0.8 inches (3.5 x 2.0 x 7.0 cm) = 2.8 inches (7.0 cm). Extra large cartridges sold separately are larger than 1.5 x 1.0 inches (3.7 x 2.5 cm) = 3.6 inches (9.25 cm) for significant time saving
        • Long Lasting: The included super premium cartridge is Lv.1 capable of irradiating up to 3 million rounds. Long life of 500,000 rounds even at maximum output Lv.10 If the product runs out, just replace the cartridge and you can use it again
        • Output Settings: The number of capacitors that greatly affect the performance of the product is incredible. You can freely adjust the intensity of the light according to your skin and the area you are using. In addition, you can choose between 1 time, 3 times and 6 consecutive modes to reduce irritation
        • High Functionality: You can choose between 3 shot modes manually, auto, and continuous. Manual mode for illumination at your own time. Automatically illuminates when the sensor senses skin. Continuous mode that can be illuminated at a maximum speed of 0.4 seconds ( Lv.1 continuous mode )
        • Range of use: Not only can it be used on the body, but also on the face, including hair of women and beards, and delicate parts such as fingers, underneath, etc. You can also use it as a beautiful face device with light using the skin care cartridge (sold separately)
